            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d69219-Hd1e108">Rubrica 2</head>
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d69219-Hd1e111" type="question-title">De medio et extremis</head>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d69219-d1e114">
              ¶ De medio et extremis. Rubrica 2.
            </p>
<!--left off here-->
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d69219-d1e119">
                <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d69219-Rd1e116">ARistoteles 
               ethicorum: li.
      2. c. 5.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d69219-Qd1e127">Medium est quod equaliter 
               distat ab vtroque extre morum. 
               Omnis sciens superabundantiam et defectum
        fugit: medium autem querit. Uirtus medii
        est coniecturatrix. Malitie quidem est 
               superabundantia et defectus: virtutis autem 
               medietas.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d69219-d1e144">/ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d69219-Rd1e142">6. c.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d69219-Qd1e146">in omnibus medietas est 
               laudanda: extrema autem non recta nec 
               laudabilia: sed vituperabilia sunt.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d69219-d1e155">/ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d69219-Rd1e155">7. c. et fi.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d69219-Qd1e157">In vno
        quoque medium accipere difficile est. Medium 
               attingere summe difficile est. Medius hintus in 
               omnibus laudabilis est.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d69219-d1e167">/ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d69219-Rd1e169">Li. 4. c. 6.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d69219-Qd1e169">Superabundantie <!--211.xml-->
        <pb ed="#V" n="86-v"/>
                  <cb ed="#V" n="a"/>
                  et defectus vituperabiles sunt.</quote>/ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d69219-Rd1e182">Li. 5. c. 3.</ref>
         <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d69219-Qd1e186">Equale est medium maioris et minoris.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d69219-d1e183">
               
               / <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d69219-Rd1e193">Idem magnorum moralium: li. i. c. 11.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d69219-Qd1e187">
               Medium habere difficile est.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d69219-d1e193">/ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d69219-Rd1e203">40. c.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d69219-Qd1e195">Optimum
        est medium.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d69219-d1e201">/ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d69219-Rd1e213">Idem politicorum: li. 3. c. 9.
         et penul.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d69219-Qd1e203">Iustum querentes medium 
               querunt.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d69219-d1e211">/ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d69219-Rd1e226">Li. 4. c. 9.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d69219-Qd1e213">Quod mediocre optimum
        est: et quod medium. Que media optima sunt.
        Paucum est quod medium semper.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d69219-d1e222">/ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d69219-Rd1e239">Li. 5. c.
        6.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d69219-Qd1e224">Quod iustum est equale videtur esse.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d69219-d1e230">
               
                / <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d69219-Rd1e252">Li. 6. c. 2.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d69219-Qd1e234">Semper querunt quod iustum et quod
        equale est: quam minores sunt: preeminentes
        autem nihil curant.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d69219-d1e242">/ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d69219-Rd1e264">Lib. 8. c. 7.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d69219-Qd1e244">Medium
        superabundantiarum laudamus et dicimus
        prosequi oportere.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d69219-d1e252">
               
               ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d69219-Rd1e278">Ouidius methamorph. lib. 2.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d69219-Qd1e256">Medio 
               tutissimus ibis.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d69219-d1e262">
               
               ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d69219-Rd1e290">Seneca tragediarum in hercule etheo. c. 6.</ref>
         <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d69219-Qd1e266">Quisquis medium defugit iter.
        Stabili nunquam tramite curret.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d69219-d1e274">
               
               ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d69219-Rd1e304">Maximianus:</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d69219-Qd1e278">Maior enim mediis 
               gratia rebus inest.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d69219-d1e285">
               
              ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d69219-Rd1e317">Heinricus samariensis: li. 2.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d69219-Qd1e289">Nec viscosa
        manus oleo nec vncta sit vno.
        Interutruque tenens respuat omne nimis.</quote>
            </p>
